      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i looked at the ELB idle timeout and it's set to 60s, which should be plenty for our traffic. it's just so frustrating because there's no clear pattern. it feels like these drops are just happening randomly, almost like there's some glitch or something hidden in the infra that we just can't see. is there any way to actually trace the packet level to see if it's being dropped by a specific rule or if it's just vanishing?",
